#: ../../../doc/en/announce/release-2.6.3.rst:2
msgid "pytest-2.6.3: fixes and little improvements"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../doc/en/announce/release-2.6.3.rst:4
msgid ""
"pytest is a mature Python testing tool with more than a 1100 tests against "
"itself, passing on many different interpreters and platforms. This release "
"is drop-in compatible to 2.5.2 and 2.6.X. See below for the changes and see "
"docs at:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../doc/en/announce/release-2.6.3.rst:9
msgid "http://pytest.org"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../doc/en/announce/release-2.6.3.rst:11
msgid "As usual, you can upgrade from pypi via::"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../doc/en/announce/release-2.6.3.rst:13
msgid "pip install -U pytest"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../doc/en/announce/release-2.6.3.rst:15
msgid "Thanks to all who contributed, among them:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../doc/en/announce/release-2.6.3.rst:17
msgid ""
"Floris Bruynooghe Oleg Sinyavskiy Uwe Schmitt Charles Cloud Wolfgang "
"Schnerring"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../doc/en/announce/release-2.6.3.rst:23
msgid "have fun, holger krekel"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../doc/en/announce/release-2.6.3.rst:27
msgid "Changes 2.6.3"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../doc/en/announce/release-2.6.3.rst:29
msgid ""
"fix issue575: xunit-xml was reporting collection errors as failures instead "
"of errors, thanks Oleg Sinyavskiy."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../doc/en/announce/release-2.6.3.rst:32
msgid ""
"fix issue582: fix setuptools example, thanks Laszlo Papp and Ronny "
"Pfannschmidt."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../doc/en/announce/release-2.6.3.rst:35
msgid ""
"Fix infinite recursion bug when pickling capture.EncodedFile, thanks Uwe "
"Schmitt."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../doc/en/announce/release-2.6.3.rst:38
msgid ""
"fix issue589: fix bad interaction with numpy and others when showing "
"exceptions.  Check for precise \"maximum recursion depth exceed\" exception "
"instead of presuming any RuntimeError is that one (implemented in py dep).  "
"Thanks Charles Cloud for analysing the issue."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../doc/en/announce/release-2.6.3.rst:43
msgid ""
"fix conftest related fixture visibility issue: when running with a CWD "
"outside of a test package pytest would get fixture discovery wrong. Thanks "
"to Wolfgang Schnerring for figuring out a reproducible example."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../doc/en/announce/release-2.6.3.rst:47
msgid ""
"Introduce pytest_enter_pdb hook (needed e.g. by pytest_timeout to cancel the "
"timeout when interactively entering pdb).  Thanks Wolfgang Schnerring."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../doc/en/announce/release-2.6.3.rst:50
msgid ""
"check xfail/skip also with non-python function test items. Thanks Floris "
"Bruynooghe."
msgstr ""
